{"tid":341670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老共狗] 市民被拒延期交保證金 申DQ朱凱廸鄭松泰案擱置","createTime":"2017-07-31T03:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T04:07:20.000Z","uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f64ccb00fdeda6e78c23c01e0af64925467b407","tid":341670,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:43:04.000Z","msg":"政府提出司法覆核議員宣誓效力，法庭至今判定六名民主派議員喪失議席，另外市民羅景楊今年3月按《立法會條例》第73條提出的訴訟挑戰朱凱廸及鄭松泰就職宣誓效力，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但一直遲遲未有按要求交出2萬元訟費保證金。</strong></span>法官區慶祥今頒下判詞，指申請人不合理延遲，亦沒有良好理由說服法庭行使酌情權，申請DQ朱凱廸及鄭松泰的案件將繼續擱置（stay），<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>法官並下令申請人羅景楊須支付訟費。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死廢老2萬蚊都俾唔起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24442766fc1eda1a4b71ab00f7dc60cc11526be2","tid":341670,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/114401_68941b188a53a77b2be458c474be9ff8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F114401_68941b188a53a77b2be458c474be9ff8.jpg&h=95f3851c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c49662677ab50660f564f3b0215eb4fde4375b7","tid":341670,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205eede987ffec6ceb5ed1aef317be9b6ac4c417","tid":341670,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"咁係咪應該唔會搬番出黎"},{"pid":"b8508969945d5326329a63682fc4174d56bc544d","tid":341670,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"